(9, 'Message from the Management Team', 'Message from the Management Team', '経営陣からのメッセージ', '<p>We will support the realization of the dream process of the company.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now, Myanmar has entered an era of dramatic economic change. This change, companies are faced with a variety of problems to be solved with an increase in competition. We, I want to be a professional company to contribute to the success of Myanmar companies. Main Our goal is the advancement of client companies. It does not is that it of performing advice to clients simply.<br />\r\nIt is to help realistically the customers in that it transferred to practice the management theory necessary for business development, and progress. We believe &quot;company that successfully meet the market needs, and progress has been made ​​has put in the hands of their own achievements that market share and profits,&quot; he said. Our mission is to lead to success in the business of corporate customers through a service such as our. We will provide the available training services and consulting services to clients to think I want to make the customer, and want to improve the productivity of the various businesses.</p>\r\n', '<p>MJBC သည္ သင့္ကုမၸဏီဧ။္ လုပ္ငန္းအၾကံအစည္မ်ားကုိ လက္ေတြ႕ အေကာင္အထည္ေပၚေအာင္ကူညီေဆာင္ရြက္ေပးေနပါသည္။</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now, Myanmar has entered an era of dramatic economic change. This change, companies are faced with a variety of problems to be solved with an increase in competition. We, I want to be a professional company to contribute to the success of Myanmar companies. Main Our goal is the advancement of client companies. It does not is that it of performing advice to clients simply.<br />\r\nIt is to help realistically the customers in that it transferred to practice the management theory necessary for business development, and progress. We believe &quot;company that successfully meet the market needs, and progress has been made ​​has put in the hands of their own achievements that market share and profits,&quot; he said. Our mission is to lead to success in the business of corporate customers through a service such as our. We will provide the available training services and consulting services to clients to think I want to make the customer, and want to improve the productivity of the various businesses.</p>\r\n', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.4rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: ''Glober SemiBold Free''; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2rem; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; letter-spacing: 0.05rem; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">私たちは、会社の夢のプロセスの実現をサポートします。</font></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.4rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: ''Glober SemiBold Free''; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2rem; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; letter-spacing: 0.05rem; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">さて、ミャンマーは劇的な経済的変化の時代に突入してきた。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">この変更は、企業が競争の増加に伴って、解決すべきさまざまな問題に直面している。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">私たちは、私がミャンマー会社の成功に貢献する専門の会社になりたい。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">メイン私たちの目標は、顧客企業の発展である。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">これは、クライアントに助言を行うこと、それが単に。ということではありません</font></font><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">、それはビジネスの開発、進歩のために必要な経営理論を実践に移すことで、お客様に現実的に支援することです。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">私たちは信じている」に成功し、市場のニーズを満たす会社を、そして進歩が市場シェアと利益という自らの成果を手に入れている行われている&quot;と彼は言った。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">私たちの使命は、私たちのようなサービスを通じて顧客企業のビジネスの成功につながることがある。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">当社は、利用可能なトレーニングサービスを提供し、私は顧客を作りたいと思うようにクライアントにコンサルティングサービス、各種ビジネスの生産性を向上させることになるでしょう。</font></font></p>\r\n');

