(2, 'What will help to customers?', 'Customers ကုိကူညီႏုိင္သည့္ အခ်က္အလက္မ်ား', '何が顧客に役立つのだろうか？', '<p>MJBC will help to make your business growth a reality. Our mission is to help you achieve your dreams. Many Myanmar companies face various kinds of problems and issues.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We can positively support the solving of these problems issues at your company. As management professionals, we support Myanmar manufacturing companies to improve safety, quality, delivery, costs, and productivity. We support Myanmar service companies to improve how to welcome visitors and upgrade sales skills.<br />\r\nWe support Myanmar companies to improve financial results and increase the amount of sales. As consultants, our joy is to help you to realize your dreams.</p>\r\n', '<p>MJBC က သင့္လုပ္ငန္းကုိ အမွန္တကယ္ ေအာင္ျမင္ေအာင္ကူညီေပးႏုိင္ပါသည္။</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ကြ်ႏု္ပ္တုိ႕ဧ။္ အဓိကရည္ရြယ္ခ်က္မွာ သင္ဧ။္ အိမ္မက္ေတြကုိ အေကာင္အထည္ေဖာ္ေပးရန္ျဖစ္ပါသည္။</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MJBC will help to make your business growth a reality. Our mission is to help you achieve your dreams. Many Myanmar companies face various kinds of problems and issues.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We can positively support the solving of these problems issues at your company. As management professionals, we support Myanmar manufacturing companies to improve safety, quality, delivery, costs, and productivity. We support Myanmar service companies to improve how to welcome visitors and upgrade sales skills.<br />\r\nWe support Myanmar companies to improve financial results and increase the amount of sales. As consultants, our joy is to help you to realize your dreams.</p>\r\n', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.4rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: ''Glober SemiBold Free''; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2rem; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; letter-spacing: 0.05rem; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">MJBCは、あなたのビジネスの成長を実現させるのに役立ちます。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">私たちの使命は、あなたの夢を達成するの​​を助けることです。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">多くのミャンマー企業が問題点や課題の様々な種類に直面しています。</font></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.4rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: ''Glober SemiBold Free''; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2rem; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; letter-spacing: 0.05rem; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">私たちは積極的にあなたの会社で、これらの問題の問題の解決をサポートすることができます。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">経営の専門家として、私たちは、安全性、品質、納期、コスト、生産性を向上させるためにミャンマーの製造会社をサポートしています。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">私たちは、訪問者を歓迎し、営業スキルをアップグレードする方法を改善するためにミャンマーサービス企業をサポートしています。</font></font><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">私たちは、ミャンマーの企業が決算を改善し、売上高の量を増加させるためにサポートしています。</font><font class="goog-text-highlight" style="box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-box-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 170) 2px 2px 4px; box-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 170) 2px 2px 4px; position: relative; background-color: rgb(201, 215, 241);">コンサルタントとして、私たちの喜びがあなたの夢を実現するお手伝いをすることです。</font></font></p>\r\n'),
(6, 'What is consulting?', 'အတုိင္ပင္ခံလုပ္ငန္း ဆုိတာဘာလဲ?', 'コンサルティングとは何ですか？', '<p>1. Customized consulting courses<br />\r\n* What we do<br />\r\nWe supply consulting services based on your needs, using our specialists&rsquo; know-how of each field.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Fees<br />\r\nAfter first having a free initial consultation to discuss the client&rsquo;s needs and expectations, we estimate a reasonable price depending on the size and condition of the client&rsquo;s company and on the time needed and results expected. This initial consultation is without cost.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Group consulting courses<br />\r\n* What we do<br />\r\nThe purpose of group consulting courses is to solve the common problems and issues of participating companies. For examples; ・Introduction of 3S management system or visual management, etc. ・Revision and design of human resources management system ・Improvement of hospitality services and sales management, etc. ・Improvement of logistic management, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Fees<br />\r\nFees are reasonable because representatives from several companies attend. Compared to customized courses, the group consulting course fee is about one &ndash; third of the cost.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Monthly advisory contracts<br />\r\nIn addition to the courses above, we also supply monthly advisory contracts. This service is suited to companies wanting to resolve a wide range of problems and issues.<br />\r\nClients wanting to concentrate on pinpoint problems should choose customized or group consulting courses, as described in numbers 1 and 2 above .</p>\r\n', '<p>၁. စိတ္ၾကိဳက္ အတုိင္ပင္ခံလုပ္ငန္း သင္တန္းမ်ား<br />\r\n* ကြ်နုပ္တို႔ ဝန္ေဆာင္မႈမ်ား</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We supply consulting services based on your needs, using our specialists&rsquo; know-how of each field.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Fees<br />\r\nAfter first having a free initial consultation to discuss the client&rsquo;s needs and expectations, we estimate a reasonable price depending on the size and condition of the client&rsquo;s company and on the time needed and results expected. This initial consultation is without cost.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Group consulting courses<br />\r\n* What we do<br />\r\nThe purpose of group consulting courses is to solve the common problems and issues of participating companies. For examples; ・Introduction of 3S management system or visual management, etc. ・Revision and design of human resources management system ・Improvement of hospitality services and sales management, etc. ・Improvement of logistic management, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Fees<br />\r\nFees are reasonable because representatives from several companies attend. Compared to customized courses, the group consulting course fee is about one &ndash; third of the cost.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Monthly advisory contracts<br />\r\nIn addition to the courses above, we also supply monthly advisory contracts. This service is suited to companies wanting to resolve a wide range of problems and issues.<br />\r\nClients wanting to concentrate on pinpoint problems should choose customized or group consulting courses, as described in numbers 1 and 2 above .</p>\r\n', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.4rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: ''Glober SemiBold Free''; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2rem; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; letter-spacing: 0.05rem; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">1.カスタマイズされたコンサルティングコースは</font></font><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">*私たちは何をすべきか</font></font><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">私たちは、各分野のスペシャリスト」のノウハウを使って、あなたのニーズに基づいたコンサルティングサービスを提供します。</font></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.4rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: ''Glober SemiBold Free''; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2rem; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; letter-spacing: 0.05rem; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">*料金は</font></font><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">最初のクライアントのニーズや期待を議論する自由な最初の相談をした後、私たちはクライアントの会社の規模や状況に、必要に応じて、結果は予想時間に応じて合理的な価格を見積もる。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">この最初の相談はコストなしである。</font></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.4rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: ''Glober SemiBold Free''; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2rem; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; letter-spacing: 0.05rem; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">2.グループコンサルティングコース</font></font><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">*私たちはやる</font></font><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">グループコンサルティングコースの目的は、参加企業の共通の問題や課題を解決することである。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">例については、</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">3S管理システムや視覚的な管理の導入&middot;等&middot;改訂および人事管理システムの設計&middot;などのホスピタリティ&middot;サービスおよび販売管理の向上&middot;物流管理の改善など</font></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.4rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: ''Glober SemiBold Free''; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2rem; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; letter-spacing: 0.05rem; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">*手数料</font></font><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">いくつかの企業の代表者が出席しているため料金が合理的である。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">カスタマイズされたコースと比較すると、グループのコンサルティングコースの料金は約1である-コストのサード。</font></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.4rem; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: ''Glober SemiBold Free''; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2rem; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; letter-spacing: 0.05rem; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">3.毎月の顧問契約</font></font><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">上記のコースに加えて、我々はまた、毎月の顧問契約を供給。</font><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">このサービスは、問題点や課題の広い範囲を解決したい企業に適しています。</font></font><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\r\n<font style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;">クライアントは、ピンポイントの問題に集中したい番号1と上記2に記載したように、カスタマイズされたまたはグループコンサルティングコースを選択する必要があります。</font></font></p>\r\n'),
